---
title: "US58 — Manage expert categories"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Admin
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>CategoriesScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpsertExpertCategory
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: create / rename / suspend a category
  B->>C: save(category)
  C->>G: insert/update expert_categories
  G-->>C: ok
  C-->>B: catalog updated
  B-->>A: marketplace filters reflect it
